INSTALLATION STEPS
https://github.com/mgonzalo96/esdc
########################################
CLIENT SIDE
#########################################

For the near real time web page:

to install an application server (Tomcat) and use the nrtsaa-1.1.html
web page.

to alocate in the same directory the followings folder: 'dist', 'lib' and 'src'.

_________________________________________

For the interactive web page:

to install an application server (Tomcat) and use the form-1.1.html
web page.

to alocate in the same directory the followings folder: 'dist', 'lib' and 'src'.


########################################
SERVER SIDE
#########################################

install node on the server and run app2ports-0.0.4.js
and also the splunk-sdk library.

important:
var splunkjs = require('/home/esdcops/mysplunk/node_modules/splunk-sdk');

change this directory in your computer.
